{
  "texts": [
    "Our prior research, this study demonstrates that generative AI can convey positive emotional experiences to consumers.",
    "In essence, generative AI demonstrates a form of artificial empathy, marking a significant step forward for the next generation of AI in marketing communications (Liu-Thompkins et al. 2022).",
    "At last, the current paper sheds light on how different aspects of experiential narratives impact consumer intended engagement.",
    "It suggests that the level of embodied cognition and the diversity of sensory language have a more substantial effect on positive consumer attitudes and engagement than positive affect.",
    "Our findings highlight some implications of the growing use of generative AI by firms to create a massive amount of marketing content at a lower cost."
  ]
}